room_title: Escape room "The Attic" by Wichita Room Escape in Wichita
room_description: After stopping by your childhood home, you're surprised that your eccentric Aunt Martha isn't around. Upon hearing a noise in the attic, you go up to investigate--immediately after entering the attic, the door locks behind you! While looking for a way out, you begin to uncover your family's long list of treasures and secrets.
